patterns.title: Mini-Dino
patterns.description:
Mini-Dino is made by crocheting each part individually and then sewing them together. Color changes will be indicated with color-coded text.

Materials:

About 20g of size 4 worsted weight yarn for the main color
About 5g of size 4 worsted weight yarn for the stripe color
4mm crochet hook
Yarn needle
Scissors
6mm safety eyes
Stuffing
patterns.author: MerryMakes

patterns.description: The pattern for this shabby-chic bed came about when our family was recently adopted by a little orange stray tabby. Its a simple pattern, but uses an interesting technique to ensure that the right side is on the inside bottom of the bed, but switches to the outside walls, while still remaining a seamless pattern. Give it a try, and give your favorite kitty a cozy place to take his naps!

patterns.title: Dog Coat
patterns.author: Yarnspirations Design Studio
patterns.description:
This cozy knit dog coat is perfect for small dogs who need a little extra warmth and comfort during the colder months. With simple ribbing this free knit pattern is easy to work up using thick Bernat Blanket Pet yarn. With Everfresh Probiotic Technology, this yarn is a safe and natural solution for helping reduce pet odors.

Materials:
Size U.S. 10 (6 mm) double pointed needles
Size U.S. 10 (6 mm) circular knitting needles
Stitch markers

SIZES
To fit dog chest measurement:
S 10 25.5 cm
M 14 35.5 cm
L 17 43 cm
XL 20 51 cm

Finished chest:
S 12 30.5 cm
M 16 40.6 cm
L 19 48 cm
XL 22 56 cm

patterns.description:
You knit for the joy of it, for the comfort and the beauty. patterns.title: Toe Up Simple Sock
patterns.author: Dean and Bean's Sock Machines
patterns.description:
This basic pattern features a toe up design, wrapped short row toe and heel, and hung hem. Everything can be knit on your Dean and Beans 2.0 Sock Machine - the only finishing needed is weaving in tails.

This pattern works with any size cylinder. The most common sizes for socks are 54, 60, 64, and 72 needles.

We suggest fingering weight yarn with at least 10% nylon.
